%% Diagram: Lease lifecycle — acquire, work, release or expire
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant L as Lock Service
    participant R as Resource

    C->>L: Acquire(resource, TTL=30s)
    L-->>C: Granted (expires at T+30s)
    Note over C: Work begins
    C->>R: Read / mutate
    R-->>C: Ack
    Note over C: Work continues...
    alt Releases before TTL
        C->>L: Release
        L-->>C: Released
    else TTL expires first
        Note over L: Lease auto-expires at T+30s
        Note over C: Stale holder may still be working
    end
